						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa, Parakēsarivarmaṉ, Year 8 = c. 10th Century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records a gift of 30 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tiruvāṉaikkal Perumāṉaḍigaḷ at Tiruveḷḷaṟai by Araiyan Tāḻi of the same village.</p>						

